  <prompt>Per FR-3H2.3: when edge connects two nodes whose configs don't reference each other's OutputVariable, show non-blocking warning "This edge forces sequential execution. Confirm or remove?" Advisory only.</prompt>
  <goal>Authors aware of unnecessary edges that kill parallelism. Advisory does NOT block save.</goal>
